WEBVTT

00:00:09.205 --> 00:00:11.171
"Sorry, my phone died."

00:00:11.195 --> 00:00:13.471
"It's nothing. I'm fine."

00:00:13.495 --> 00:00:16.723
"These allegations
are completely unfounded."

00:00:16.747 --> 00:00:20.100
"The company was not aware
of any wrongdoing."

00:00:21.210 --> 00:00:23.519
"I love you."

00:00:23.543 --> 00:00:26.387
We hear anywhere
from 10 to 200 lies a day,

00:00:26.411 --> 00:00:29.754
and we spent much of our history
coming up with ways to detect them,

00:00:29.778 --> 00:00:32.676
from medieval torture
devices to polygraphs,